  "title": "Core Concepts of Applying Knowledge",
  "lessonText": "In this section, we explore how to apply the core concepts of 'Gu Gu Ga Ga' in early childhood communication.",
  "data": {
    "content": "• Understanding 'Gu Gu Ga Ga' is crucial for language development in children.\n• The sounds of 'Gu Gu Ga Ga' significantly influence social interaction among young learners.\n• Engaging with 'Gu Gu Ga Ga' helps children communicate effectively with peers and adults.\n• Fill in the blanks exercise reinforces the importance of these sounds in communication.\n• Quiz questions assess comprehension of the core ideas presented in this module."
  }
